$10</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id="Soups">\r\n	<h2 class="glamor yellow">Soups</h2>\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood">CROCK OF CHILI</h4> \r\n	<p>Diced onion &amp; melted cheddar jack, w/fresh tortilla chips $7</p>\r\n\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood">FRENCH ONION</h4>\r\n	<p>with melted mozzarella $7</p>\r\n\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood">SOUP DU JOUR</h4>\r\n	<p>cup/bowl</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id="salads">\r\n	<h2 class="glamor yellow">Salads</h2>\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood">ARUGULA SALAD</h4>\r\n	<p>Baby arugula, bermuda onion, crumbled gorgonzola, chopped walnuts, sun dried cherries $14</p>\r\n\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood">CAESAR SALAD</h4>\r\n	<p>Romaine, homemade dressing &amp; croutons Sm $7 Lg $12</p>\r\n	\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood">HOUSE SALAD</h4>\r\n	<p>Lettuce, tomato, cucumber, carrot &amp; onion, Sm $6 Lg $10</p>\r\n	\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood">PORTABELLA</h4>\r\n	<p>SALAD Grilled portabella mushroom &amp; toasted garlic over mixed greens with balsamic vinaigrette $14</p>\r\n	\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood">ALE HOUSE SALAD</h4>\r\n	<p>Mixed greens, goat cheese, dried cranberries &amp; candied pecans $14</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Add on... Grilled Portabella Mushroom $5<br/>\r\n		Grilled or Blackened Chicken $5 <br/>\r\n		Grilled Fresh Salmon $7 <br/>\r\n		Sliced Steak $7 <br/>\r\n		Grilled or Blackened Shrimp (5) $8\r\n	</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id="wings">\r\n	<h2 class="glamor yellow">ALE HOUSE WINGS</h2>\r\n	<h3 class="sherwood">14 SPICE WINGS</h3>\r\n	<p>Jumbo chicken wings dry rubbed in our secret blend of 14 spices baked to perfection &amp; flash fried for extra crispiness $12</p>\r\n\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood yellow">BUFFALO</h4>\r\n	<p>Mild, Medium, or Hot</p>\r\n\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood yellow">JAMAICAN JERK</h4>\r\n	<p>Hot &amp; Spicy, served with cool ranch</p>\r\n\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood yellow">TERIYAKI</h4>\r\n	<p>Classic Asian Style</p>\r\n\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood yellow">CAJUN</h4>\r\n	<p>New Orleans Zing</p>\r\n\r\n	<h4 class="sherwood yellow">HONEY BBQ</h4